		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I mentioned how it is done and an alternative way to go about it. You toggle !CARTIN in signal on BIOS accesses to prevent bus fights or you disable BIOS ROM in the Mega CD and run BIOS from cartridge that has !CARTIN signal open.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


